# ğŸ¾ Pet Adoption Website

A full-stack **Pet Adoption Web Application** built using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Frontend)** and **Node.js, Express, MongoDB (Backend)**.  

This platform enables users to browse pets available for adoption, donate funds or supplies, volunteer for animal welfare, and contact the team.  
Admins can monitor all donations, volunteers, and contact requests through an interactive dashboard.

