ğŸ§ª API Endpoints
Method	Endpoint	Description
GET	/api/donations	Fetch all donations
POST	/api/donations/item	Add an item donation
POST	/api/donations/money	Add a monetary donation
POST	/api/contacts	Submit a contact message
POST	/api/volunteers	Register as a volunteer
GET	/api/volunteers	Retrieve volunteer data
ğŸ“Š Deployment Details
Component	Platform	URL
Frontend	Netlify	https://petadoption-hema.netlify.app

Backend	Render	https://petadoption-backend.onrender.com

